flowchart TD
    %% Déclencheurs de la pipeline
    A0[Push/PR sur main] --> CI

    subgraph CI["CI - Continuous Integration"]
        A[Checkout repository] --> B[Set up Node.js]
        B --> C[Install frontend dependencies]
        C --> D[Run frontend tests and generate coverage]
        D --> E{Tests outcome?}
        E -->|Success| F[Upload frontend coverage report]
        E -->|Failure| G[Tests failed - Block deployment]
        F --> H[Verify tests passed]
        H --> I[Build frontend Angular]
        I --> J[Upload frontend dist artifact]
        J --> K[SonarCloud Scan]
    end

    subgraph CD["CD - Continuous Deployment"]
        L[Checkout repository] --> M[Download frontend dist artifact]
        M --> N[Set up Docker Buildx]
        N --> O[Log in to GitHub Container Registry]
        O --> P[Extract metadata for Docker image]
        P --> Q[Build and push Docker image]
    end

    CI -->|needs: frontend| CD
 